docs.abstract: City workers on Thursday began removing memorials and barricades from the intersection where the police killed George Floyd just over a year ago. The unannounced effort brought hundreds of people to the scene in protest.

docs.abstract: Matthew A. Frank, one of the prosecutors in the Derek Chauvin trial, asked the judge to sentence the former police officer to three decades in prison for the ‘cruel’ killing of George Floyd.
